    <section id="id1167178467582">
      <title>LEARNING OUTCOME 1: GEOGRAPHICAL ENQUIRY</title>
      <para id="id1167173251456">The learner will be able to use enquiry skills to investigate geographical and </para>
      <para id="id1167173276721">environmental concepts and processes.</para>
      <section id="id1167176085565">
        <title>Assessment Standard</title>
        <para id="id1167178336757">We know this when the learner:</para>
        <para id="id1167173152339">1.3 identifies symbols used in different kinds of maps (including plan view, grids and map keys) [works with sources].</para>
        <para id="id1167178186911">1.4 locates places using a simple grid referencing system and directions [works with sources].</para>
